---
import LayoutBase from "../layouts/LayoutBase.astro";

---
<LayoutBase>  
      <main>
        <h1>AI Developer | Chatbot, Assistant, Agents | With ChatGPT API </h1>
            <h2>SERVERLESS CLOUD SOLUTIONS</h2>
            <h3> Transforming Data in Experiences Intelligent and Scalable</h3>
          <section id="about">
              <h2>About Me</h2>
              <img src="profile_picture.jpg" alt="Profile Picture">
              <p>Hi there! I'm an AI developer specializing in chatbots, virtual assistants, and task automation using the ChatGPT API. I also offer serverless cloud solutions and transforming data into experiences, intelligent, and scalable.</p>
              <p>With over 5 years of experience in developing AI models and deploying them on cloud infrastructure, I have a strong background in creating intelligent systems that can help businesses streamline their operations and improve customer engagement.</p>
              <p>In addition to my technical skills, I am passionate about staying up-to-date with the latest advances in AI research and development. I enjoy attending conferences and workshops, participating in online communities, and reading industry publications to continue learning and growing as a professional.</p>
          </section>
          <section id="services">
              <h2>Services</h2>
              <ul>
                  <li>Chatbot Development</li>
                  <li>Virtual Assistant Development</li>
                  <li>Agents Task Automation</li>
                  <li>Serverless Cloud Solutions (Backend)</li>
              </ul>
          </section>
          <section id="design">
              <h2>Milestones</h2>
              <ul>
                  <li>Integration APIs, WebSocket</li>
                  <li>Data Ingestion</li>
                  <li>Data Indexation</li>
                  <li>Data Consultation Interface</li>
              </ul>
          </section>
          <section id="skills">
              <h2>Skills</h2>
              <ul>
                  <li>Machine Learning (ML)</li>
                  <li>Natural Language Processing (NLP)</li>
                  <li>Large Language Model (LLM)</li>
                  <li>ChatGPT API</li>
                  <li>Programming languages: Python and Javascript</li>
                  <li>Framework: LlamaIndex, LangChain and AutoGen</li>
                  <li>APIs RESTful, GraphQL, and WebSocket</li>
                  <li>Cloud Function Lambda</li>
                  <li>Docker on serverless</li>
                  <li>Event Orchestration and Routing services</li>
                  <li>Brocker Pub/Sub and notification (API, Email, SMS and Movil)</li>
                  <li>Databases Vector, SQL and NoSQL</li>
                  <li>File Systems, Datawerhouse and Datalake</li>
                  <li>Load Balancing and Networking</li>
              </ul>
          </section>
          <section id="contact">
              <h2>Contact</h2>
              <p>If you would like to learn more about my services or discuss potential collaboration opportunities, please feel free to reach out to me via email or phone.</p>
              <p>Email: [your email address]</p>
              <p>Phone: [your phone number]</p>
          </section>
      </main>
</LayoutBase>